    • setShowTooltipTimeIntervalMs

      @NonNull public BlinkIdOverlaySettings.Builder setShowTooltipTimeIntervalMs(long showTooltipTimeIntervalMs)
      Description copied from interface: BlinkIdOverlaySettingsOptions
      Sets time interval between the start of the tilt step and displaying the help tooltip. Help tooltip is displayed only once. By default, this is set to BlinkIdOverlaySettingsOptions.DEFAULT_SHOW_TOOLTIP_TIME_INTERVAL_MS.
